参观<a href="https://www.cnbc.com/2023/09/27/uaw-leader-condemns-trump-ahead-of-michigan-visit-during-union-strike.html">一家非工会汽车零部件工厂</a>来配合拜登的举动，但在很大程度上遭到了工会领导层的忽视和嘲笑。这可能巩固了拜登作为铁锈地带和被遗忘的工人阶级捍卫者的形象。</p><p> UAW 罢工——包括要求加薪 40% 和每周工作 32 小时——是美国更普遍的劳工复兴的一部分。大规模罢工浪潮正在<a href="https://www.wsj.com/economy/jobs/labor-strikes-multiply-as-workers-score-wins-9c08060e">全国蔓延</a>，其中包括好莱坞作家和演员、美国航空和达美航空的飞行员、UPS 送货人员、拉斯维加斯服务人员，可能还有凯撒医疗机构的医护人员。到目前为止，2023年的罢工活动已经达到了自20世纪80年代以来从未出现过的水平： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9099c225-326f-40d7-8b5b-fa6e437759d3_1184x637.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9099c225-326f-40d7-8b5b-fa6e437759d3_1184x637.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9099c225-326f-40d7-8b5b-fa6e437759d3_1184x637.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9099c225-326f-40d7-8b5b-fa6e437759d3_1184x637.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9099c225-326f-40d7-8b5b-fa6e437759d3_1184x637.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9099c225-326f-40d7-8b5b-fa6e437759d3_1184x637.j